{"tid":2491640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"建制派提規範議員衣著　禁穿T恤短褲及波鞋","createTime":"2021-04-16T12:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T16:38:01.000Z","uid":230530,"like":13,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"610bf2869f0a19a4850be08c777bcdf57cd8a7d4","tid":2491640,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"立法會近日修改「議事規則」，有建制派議員提出規範議員衣著。議事規則委員會擬制訂「負面清單」，禁止議員出席會議時穿着T恤、短褲及波鞋。<br />\n<br />\n立法會近日修改「議事規則」，建制派議員提出規範議員衣著。（大公文匯全媒體資料圖片）<br />\n立法會「議事規則」第42(a)列明，議員進出立法會會場，在衣飾及舉止上須保持莊重。但對於「衣飾保持莊重」的標準，並未具體說明。以往議事堂開會，曾有時任立法會主席不滿議員經常穿着T恤出席會議，認為其衣着不尊重議會，故發出「不准穿圓領衫或T恤進行會議」指引，若議員「犯規」就被趕出議會。<br />\n<br />\n議事規則委員會除了制訂「負面清單」外，亦會建議男士應穿上整齊外套及恤衫。至於女士衣着方面暫未討論，料只要莊重、不過份暴露便可。"},{"pid":"33d6574e6f5aca7c8414097a202071b495ee33b9","tid":2491640,"uid":16719,"like":193,"dislike":16,"score":177,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQD329yDUYnH2hoa1KvgtzeZRvS1fXJDzgU9jnJRXoR99?filename=skuNP4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskuNP4G.jpg&h=fbcc5fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰博最姿整<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba748312db3cfcb838a8ff989838cc658c41b363","tid":2491640,"uid":11291,"like":202,"dislike":2,"score":200,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"不如提意埋開會時禁止訓覺"},{"pid":"90067aeb3a2994f8c49d8932c8e8ea307bacf4b7","tid":2491640,"uid":50891,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"唔比姐姐show腳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13886e55ccc23d192ac2a88ffec79797c6d4ba0d","tid":2491640,"uid":290118,"like":498,"dislike":5,"score":493,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXnCuBuU8hVsxynbGhwdmX2azAhD32Bf1SJ7XJKDkTF1u?filename=o5VpSiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5VpSiB.jpg&