":"政府班AO EO departmental grade咪又係個個著西裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec54bc57222098e1a7e1db55ddbaff182b7ab6c7","tid":2491640,"uid":76331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"其實佢地明唔明個議會<br />\n係淨番保皇黨同紫荊黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d656f1ddbd7fac9fc5baf93b7069ab09dfd401bc","tid":2491640,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"仲有開會果陣去厠所要主席批准，會議途中唔比瞓覺釣魚，問埋D弱智低能問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1b308fe5b9147c81402ada8f88c874a6d8c391","tid":2491640,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb20d8a0f4bea88ff6725804f7059757e9b1baf","tid":2491640,"uid":59158,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"是L旦啦<br />\n你鍾意著泳衣羽絨乜7 都好啦<br />\n關我地香港人L事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"又唔係呀<br />\n姐姐著泳衣開會 肯定大把連登狗公日夜cap圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4546f951bcd29a64198a6424bcb91f6199aab4","tid":2491640,"uid":314083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610bf2869f0a19a4850be08c777bcdf57cd8a7d4","tid":2491640,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"立法會近日修改「議事規則」，有建制派議員提出規範議員衣著。議事規則委員會擬制訂「負面清單」，禁止議員出席會議時穿着T恤、短褲及波鞋。<br />\n<br />\n立法會近日修改「議事規則」，建制派議員提出規範議員衣著。（大公文匯全媒體資料圖片）<br />\n立法會「議事規則」第42(a)列明，議員進出立法會會場，在衣飾及舉止上須保持莊重。但對於「衣飾保持莊重」的標準，並未具體說明。以往議事堂開會，曾有時任立法會主席不滿議員經常穿着T恤出席會議，認為其衣着不尊重議會，故發出「不准穿圓領衫或T恤進行會議」指引，若議員「犯規」就被趕出議會。<br />\n<br />\n議事規則委員會除了制訂「負面清單」外，亦會建議男士應穿上整齊外套及恤衫。至於女士衣着方面暫未討論，料只要莊重、不過份暴露便可。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"解散咗佢啦，仲扮咩有議會。呢台戲中国比錢?"},{"pid":"0537981d90cd98e9ef9078ee8bc8e7c019be8bff","tid":2491640,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVbJtNa8uV8fhh2mqMmz7ggvBb4F7TAzi7tTFCrsbn9Hj?filename=T4ENQWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4ENQWh.jpg&h=c3ccff29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b47f36f3b2a2fd4610384cdea527f729b6d8c2e9","tid":2491640,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXNHRSF9eT2Sj5x46htz6P6AJQpLgowSwWHWeKEXxdWx7?filename=fYUJ8JA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYUJ8JA.png&h=97b3a091&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7d0ecad2ff843e2af85194ee83f64992c086bd0","tid":2491640,"uid":316979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba748312db3cfcb838a8ff989838cc658c41b363","tid":2491640,"uid":11291,"like":202,"dislike":2,"score":200,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"不如提意埋開會時禁止訓覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"禁止睇鹹片"},{"pid":"64284b78a328cb06df308e379e36e6dcc406c574","tid":2491640,"uid":276639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"索性規定全裸咪得, 唔洗禁衫禁鞋咁煩"},{"pid":"6e9cf6ec4554d117c2d7e8a71962eff88d442b39","tid":2491640,"uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37a2a9d4ed860a97463c065f493e20349e4004c1","tid":2491640,"uid":77196,"like":139,"dislike":2,"score":137,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"至於<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">女士衣着方面暫未討論</span></span></strong>，料只要莊重、不過份暴露便可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平機會？男就列明要著乜，女嘅唔洗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"有咩幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6412be577b8b94144fc084c358b0e54dcf32f26","tid":2491640,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s